# Public repo: deny everything by default, then explicitly allow only the plugin
# files we intend to publish. This keeps References/, other people's plugins,
# design notes, and anything private out unless it is un-ignored below. Verify
# with `git ls-files` before pushing.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/LICENSE
!/README.md
!/Aardwolf Inventory Window/
/Aardwolf Inventory Window/*
!/Aardwolf Inventory Window/Epsilon_Inventory_Monitor.xml
!/Aardwolf Inventory Window/README.md
